org.apache.flink.types

Class MapValue<K extends Value,V extends Value>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.types.MapValue<K,V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - Type of the map's key element.
    V - Type of the map's value element.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Map<K,V>, IOReadableWritable, Value

    public abstract class MapValue<K extends Value,V extends Value>
extends Object
implements Value, Map<K,V>
    Generic map base type for PACT programs that implements the Value and Map interfaces. PactMap encapsulates a Java HashMap object.
    See Also:
    Value, Map, HashMap, Serialized Form
